{"tid":2244892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀錦麗團隊2助手確診    暫停競選活動3天","createTime":"2020-10-15T23:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T00:08:59.000Z","uid":204533,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9a539421d8eb8eeef6ad1c74febae3bac9cf7b","tid":2244892,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n賀錦麗原訂今天走訪北卡羅萊納州出席造勢活動，結果競選陣營今早宣布賀錦麗的通訊主任艾倫（Liz Allen），和一名職員都確診武漢肺炎（COVID-19），因此活動取消。而賀錦麗即日起到周日的面對面競選活動也將暫停。<br />\n<br />\n團隊表示，拜登上一次跟賀錦麗共同出席活動，是本月8日在亞歷桑那州，兩人同處時間約數小時，雖然新確診染疫的人員也曾出席該場活動，<strong><span class=\"red\">不過拜登沒有曝露在被傳染的風險，賀錦麗也沒有跟該職員有近距離接觸。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">競選團隊表示，賀錦麗昨天（14日）的新型冠狀病毒檢測結果為陰性</span></strong>。她將於下周一（19日）重新恢復拜票活動。（張翠蘭／綜合外電報導）</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201015/7NVTOHVBDBEDBPZIZJWPHRCNDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2F7NVTOHVBDBEDBPZIZJWPHRCNDY%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=e13eaddb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2F7NVTOHVBDBEDBPZIZJWPHRCNDY%2F&h=97655b98\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201015/7NVTOHVBDBEDBPZIZJWPHRCNDY/</a>"},{"pid":"75f887a91024c496968ddf7d383f20ee2d9d35a1","tid":2244892,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:08:18.000Z","msg":"Kamala Harris&rsquo;s comms director and flight crew member test positive for coronavirus, prompting campaign to cancel all travel<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-election/kamala-harris-staffer-coronavirus-2020-election-campaign-liz-allen-b1048459.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fus-election%2Fkamala-harris-staffer-coronavirus-2020-election-campaign-liz-allen-b1048459.html&d=